  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225090/extras/e59812d41ac0c5760456f32a48a40c05.avif?t=1766035397\" width=600 height=150 /></span>Survive in a foreign world using your creativity to assemble your defense</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225090/extras/aab3b43f74069cdbf9dc0f4c29c74e9c.avif?t=1766035397\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Risk reward - leave your base to acquire resources but run the risk of it being destroyed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use an intuitive building system to employ creative solutions as the enemy threat increases</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225090/extras/fd22a8997286cfe30b00c20ea64912f2.avif?t=1766035397\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock a variety of weapons, abilities, and upgrades to help you take out waves of enemies</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steam Version Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Friend leaderboard - compete with friends to see who can survive the longest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam cloud saves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225090/extras/e59812d41ac0c5760456f32a48a40c05.avif?t=1766035397\" width=600 height=150 /></span>Survive in a foreign world using your creativity to assemble your defense</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225090/extras/aab3b43f74069cdbf9dc0f4c29c74e9c.avif?t=1766035397\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Risk reward - leave your base to acquire resources but run the risk of it being destroyed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use an intuitive building system to employ creative solutions as the enemy threat increases</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225090/extras/fd22a8997286cfe30b00c20ea64912f2.avif?t=1766035397\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock a variety of weapons, abilities, and upgrades to help you take out waves of enemies</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steam Version Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Friend leaderboard - compete with friends to see who can survive the longest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam cloud saves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
